d to be seated behind a large, long table.\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 325, \"end\": 338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"score\": 0.9999897744159937, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Barbara Butch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\"}, {\"begin\": 399, \"end\": 409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicky_Doll\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nicky Doll\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicky_Doll\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicky_Doll\"}, {\"begin\": 432, \"end\": 438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9595811617599354, \"rank\": 0.03945707772865534, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one moment\", \"from\": 279, \"to\": 289}, {\"ngram\": \"the hours-long parade\", \"from\": 293, \"to\": 314}, {\"ngram\": \"a large group\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 372}, {\"ngram\": \"drag queens\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 387}, {\"ngram\": \"the host\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 419}, {\"ngram\": \"a tableau\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 461}, {\"ngram\": \"a large, long table\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some viewers quickly drew comparisons between the tableau and Leonardo da Vinci's iconic paintingThe Last Supper, which then drew ire from conservative Christians who called the performance disrespectful and even \\\"blasphemous.\\\"\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 595, \"end\": 612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1291450307843317e-16, \"text\": \"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \