m\": 1434, \"to\": 1447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an interview with theAssociated Press,the show's artistic director Thomas Jolly defended the tableau, saying that he wanted the performance to represent the \\\"the right to love each other, as we want and with who we want.\\\"\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1679, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1525, \"end\": 1531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"score\": 0.7742778825571619, \"rank\": 0.2849719836407086, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1470}, {\"ngram\": \"theAssociated Press\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1495}, {\"ngram\": \"the show's artistic director\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"the tableau\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1558}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1597}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"the right\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My wish is not to be subversive, nor to mock or to shock.\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1738, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My wish\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1688}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of all, I wanted to send a message of love, a message of inclusion and not at all to divide.\\\"\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1837, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1778}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1786}, {\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1797}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusion\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympicsspokesperson Anne Descamps answered a question during a Sunday press conference about the backlash to the performance,sayingthat neither the International Olympic Committee (IOC) nor Jolly had any \\\"intention to show disrespect to